label: McLaughlin Brothers Papers
description: Description This collection contains letters, post cards, invitations, and other correspondence from 1879-1886, of two brothers attending Georgetown, William L. McLaughlin, a Georgetown College and law school graduate, and Daniel Joseph McLaughlin, a Georgetown College graduate. Also included are law school notes and other school work of William L. McLaughlin and correspondence of William L. McLaughlinâ€™s daughter, Mary McLaughlin.
